"Apri la <link linkend=\"network_neighborhood_browser_mounting\">finestra per "
"il montaggio</link>."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:926
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configure &smb4k;..."
msgstr "Configura &smb4k;..."

#. Tag: para
